issue.title: Swap Hokuyo for Velodyne on X2?

content.raw:
Yes, I think I can help.

I'm assuming, based on the "access denied" message, that you cloned this repo, added your changes, and are now trying to push your changes upstream. What you'll have to do is fork this repo, make your changes, and then submit a pull request from your fork.

Let me know if my assumption is off base.
